A late 10th century grey <a href="/wiki/Sandstone" title="Sandstone">sandstone</a> and<a href="/wiki/Celadon" title="Celadon">celadon</a>-glazed pitcher from the <a href="/wiki/Song_Dynasty" title="Song Dynasty">Song Dynasty</a> (960–1279); the spout is in the form of a <i><a href="/wiki/Fenghuang" title="Fenghuang">fenghuang</a></i> head.</div>
