<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Chain_drive,_Su_Song%27s_book_of_1092.jpg" class="image" title="The endless power-transmitting chain drive from Su Song's book of 1094 describing his clock tower[208]"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Chain_drive%2C_Su_Song%27s_book_of_1092.jpg/180px-Chain_drive%2C_Su_Song%27s_book_of_1092.jpg" width="180" height="345" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
