By the 13th century, the Chinese used the <a href="/wiki/Blow-fly" title="Blow-fly">blow-fly</a> as an agent to solve murder cases in early <a href="/wiki/Forensic_entomology" title="Forensic entomology">forensic entomology</a></div>
</div>
