A modern <a href="/wiki/Geothermal_power" title="Geothermal power">geothermal borehole</a>; the Chinese dug boreholes since the <a href="/wiki/Han_Dynasty" title="Han Dynasty">Han Dynasty</a> (202 BC–220 AD) to collect <a href="/wiki/Natural_gas" title="Natural gas">natural gas</a> as fuel for boiling <a href="/wiki/Brine" title="Brine">brine</a> in producing <a href="/wiki/Salt" title="Salt">salt</a>.</div>
</div>
