<div style="right:10px; display:none;" class="metadata topicon" id="featured-star">
<div><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Featured_lists" title="This is a featured list. Click here for more information."><img alt="Featured list" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/60/LinkFA-star.png" width="14" height="14" border="0" /></a></div>
